Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.35,0:00:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}After the incident at the audition...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:01.67,0:00:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...things were awkward between Takuto and me.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:02.89,0:00:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So, I couldn't go home.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:04.69,0:00:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki said that she would make sure I'd go back.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:07.23,0:00:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We weren't too eager at first, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:09.07,0:00:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...thanks to Mitsuki's hard work...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:11.09,0:00:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I was able to make up with Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:14.24,0:00:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}To celebrate the rebirth of the combo...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:15.49,0:00:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...we launched some spectacular Spring Onion Ramen fireworks that went {\i1}boom{\i0} !
Dialogue: 2,0:00:17.91,0:00:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It felt so good!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, then...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.07,0:00:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I wonder what's going to happen today.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.87,0:00:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:27.64,0:00:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,460)}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.09,0:00:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,460)}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:38.89,0:00:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's no trace of your cancer...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:41.81,0:00:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How does it look?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:42.81,0:00:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is it all right for her to go back to work?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:46.65,0:00:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's true that if you look at her body when she's twelve...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.32,0:00:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and then look at her body when she's sixteen, it's like she isn't sick at all.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:54.28,0:00:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So, how about it?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:57.08,0:00:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:00.33,0:01:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}As long as she doesn't push herself...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:02.75,0:01:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(200,450)}All right! {Mitsuki}
Dialogue: 2,0:01:03.25,0:01:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\an1\be1\pos(45,450)}All right! {Ooshige}
Dialogue: 2,0:01:04.71,0:01:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Isn't that great, Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:06.58,0:01:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:07.17,0:01:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wakaouji-sensei.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:09.17,0:01:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I promise.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:10.34,0:01:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I won't push myself too hard!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:14.55,0:01:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Dr. Wakaouji...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:15.68,0:01:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\an1\be1\pos(75,450)}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:17.01,0:01:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\an3\be1\pos(565,450)}Thank you very much! {split on plain, keep the same on colored}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.81,0:01:25.77,Episode Title,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\pos(320,340)\bord2.5}New Feelings
Dialogue: 2,0:01:26.19,0:01:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:27.23,0:01:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...isn't this great?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:29.27,0:01:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You can sing your songs as {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}  again.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:32.24,0:01:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:33.91,0:01:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But best of all...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:34.78,0:01:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...Wakaouji-sensei forgave me...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:36.82,0:01:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That makes me really happy!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:38.30,0:01:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:41.66,0:01:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Something wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:42.80,0:01:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:44.21,0:01:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're Takuto-kun, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:46.75,0:01:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yessiree.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:47.96,0:01:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then... the bunny next to you is...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:50.05,0:01:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm Meroko!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:51.93,0:01:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, I see...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:54.01,0:01:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:55.17,0:01:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This feels like a bad dream that I still haven't woken up from.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:58.93,0:02:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:00.43,0:02:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Calling this a bad dream...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:01.85,0:02:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...that makes us sound like ghosts or demons...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:04.64,0:02:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Despite the fact that we're obviously Shinigami!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:07.84,0:02:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Shinigami?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:09.90,0:02:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So that's what it was...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:11.19,0:02:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:12.19,0:02:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko, now's not the time for that.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:14.36,0:02:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:15.62,0:02:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:16.53,0:02:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why does she know about us?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What happened while I was gone?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:21.75,0:02:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It couldn't be helped!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:23.52,0:02:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Things just happened to turn out this way.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:26.29,0:02:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:27.59,0:02:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It feels like the situation always just takes us along for the ride...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:31.26,0:02:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:32.29,0:02:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is this okay for Spring Onion Ramen?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:34.56,0:02:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}W-Well... if that's the case...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:36.71,0:02:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's fine since you've been helping out Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:39.09,0:02:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Starting now, Mitsuki's health is our biggest concern.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:42.80,0:02:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you, Ooshige-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:44.73,0:02:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's give it our all!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:46.27,0:02:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:48.19,0:02:49.19,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm finally...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:49.19,0:02:51.23,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...going back to work, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:54.07,0:02:55.46,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I have to do my best!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:59.20,0:03:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I heard that it was really fun last time...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:00.16,0:03:02.66,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah. Good morning, Tokoroki-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:02.97,0:03:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, Ooshige-chan!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's been a while.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:05.71,0:03:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon{\i0}  is coming back to work today.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:07.92,0:03:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\an1\be1\pos(30,450)}Please treat us kindly!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:09.56,0:03:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(340,450)}Please treat us kindly! {Split on plain, leave unchanged on color}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:11.21,0:03:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... now that you mention it, that's right...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:13.46,0:03:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, are you feeling better now?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:16.13,0:03:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry for causing so much trouble!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:19.04,0:03:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's fine... just watch your health.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:21.68,0:03:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:22.44,0:03:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Excuse us, then.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:24.02,0:03:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Excuse us.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:28.06,0:03:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They said it was because of poor health...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:30.06,0:03:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wonder what the real reason was.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:32.23,0:03:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:33.33,0:03:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's rumored that she has a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:35.68,0:03:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They say she doesn't even deny it herself.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:38.66,0:03:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's sure got guts.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No shame at all, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh? Is that so?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:45.50,0:03:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But, who'd you hear that rumor from?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:48.33,0:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, that's...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:52.21,0:03:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sasaki-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:53.42,0:03:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:54.28,0:03:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She comes back today, right? {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}, that is.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:57.09,0:03:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:57.68,0:03:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Looks like it.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:59.05,0:04:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Today she's at a recording for a TV music program.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:03.60,0:04:06.77,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The rumor about her skipping the audition like that...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.77,0:04:09.08,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...it's already spread everywhere in the business.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:09.94,0:04:12.15,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If she thinks she can come back that easily...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:12.15,0:04:13.59,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...she's mistaken.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:13.59,0:04:14.61,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Or, you could say...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:14.61,0:04:16.36,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I won't let her.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good morning!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:21.85,0:04:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:22.58,0:04:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's here.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:27.28,0:04:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Isn't that wonderful... she has a boyfriend...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:30.12,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Slacking off from work... must be more important.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just 'cause she's a little popular, it's gone to her head...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Even though she's a new artist... how naive...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:38.55,0:04:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What an unpleasant atmosphere.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:40.39,0:04:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just ignore them, Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:42.35,0:04:43.78,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:44.72,0:04:47.32,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is what it's like on the day back, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}His name's Eichi-kun.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:51.98,0:04:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.19,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How do they know that?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's with this?!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:56.31,0:04:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can't take it!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You! Don't just sit there!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Give them an earful! {missing line}
Dialogue: 2,0:05:00.73,0:05:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:01.61,0:05:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yo.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:02.53,0:05:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good morning.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takasu-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:05.14,0:05:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Congratulations on your return.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh? Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:09.20,0:05:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I was surprised when I heard you'd collapsed.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:12.08,0:05:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're back today... good luck!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:14.39,0:05:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takasu-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Such a wonderful bouquet...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:20.13,0:05:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow, they smell so good!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:22.05,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, I figured they'd cheer you up.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:25.64,0:05:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's almost time...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:26.93,0:05:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Shall we get going?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:27.55,0:05:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:31.44,0:05:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then... good luck!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:32.69,0:05:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:38.65,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That old guy... unexpectedly, \Nhe has a good side to him.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:41.48,0:05:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep, I was pretty surprised.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:42.95,0:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But still... {Shani: Grave mistake if Ooshige is picking up from where Meroko and Takuto ended. She shouldn't be able to hear what they were saying because they were in Shinigami forms. Maikka...}
Dialogue: 2,0:05:44.32,0:05:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What is it, Ooshige-san?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:46.45,0:05:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The rumor about Eichi-kun has spread a lot more than I thought it would...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:50.69,0:05:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:51.73,0:05:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hopefully, it won't be a big scandal...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:55.08,0:05:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's the problem?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:58.62,0:05:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Isn't that okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:59.80,0:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If there's a little scandal...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:02.13,0:06:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...then Eichi-kun will definitely find Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:05.34,0:06:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You could think about it that way too, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:07.73,0:06:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't always think this, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:10.36,0:06:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you're the type of girl who doesn't let a setback keep her down.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:13.26,0:06:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I guess so.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:14.88,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wait! That's a compliment, right?!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:17.17,0:06:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:18.05,0:06:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah... well, let's just leave it at that.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And then...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:23.49,0:06:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takasu-san talked with her...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:25.72,0:06:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:30.24,0:06:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What is this?!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:31.60,0:06:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why is it going so well for her?!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:34.15,0:06:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why are they so willing to forget what happened?!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:37.12,0:06:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She hasn't had to work hard at all...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If it were me...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:41.72,0:06:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...things wouldn't go so well.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:43.97,0:06:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wouldn't be welcomed by everyone.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:47.89,0:06:49.22,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I know...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.83,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Because... the whole world...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:51.83,0:06:54.16,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...has always been cold to me...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:13.04,0:07:14.62,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}{\c&HD3D3D3&}I wonder if she's lost...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:17.75,0:07:18.58,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:19.29,0:07:20.21,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.04,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.05,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:23.05,0:07:25.00,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}How much farther do you have to go?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.51,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}Well, you see...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:26.51,0:07:29.78,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}I'm trying to get to my grandchild's house here on this map.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:30.35,0:07:32.77,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}If that's where you're going, I know where it is.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:32.77,0:07:34.93,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}Granny, I'll take you there.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:48.99,0:07:50.44,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}Good morning!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:50.99,0:07:53.32,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}Morning? Do you know what time it is?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.87,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.28,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}You're an hour late.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.47,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}Do you want to quit?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:57.96,0:07:59.13,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:59.13,0:08:00.77,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}I'll go get ready right away!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:01.13,0:08:02.55,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:02.55,0:08:04.40,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}We've already found a replacement.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.48,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}You don't need to come anymore.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:10.22,0:08:11.40,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}{\c&HD3D3D3&}No way...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:12.93,0:08:14.76,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}What were you doing?!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:14.76,0:08:15.79,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}That's 'cause...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:15.79,0:08:18.56,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}There was an old lady who was lost...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.84,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}You know...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:19.84,0:08:22.56,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}In this world, you have to put yourself first.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.48,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}If you worry about other people...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:24.48,0:08:26.79,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}...you'll never be able to reach the top.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:31.41,0:08:32.53,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}After that...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:32.53,0:08:35.08,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...a rumor started about me being stuck up... {and you made it true}
Dialogue: 2,0:08:35.08,0:08:36.91,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and job after job was canceled.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:37.71,0:08:40.27,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Even though I was only doing the right thing...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:45.96,0:08:47.02,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I won't forgive her.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.15,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:49.72,0:08:51.93,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I've come so far since then...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:51.93,0:08:54.73,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I've had to go through so much...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:54.73,0:08:56.47,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}After failing once...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:56.47,0:08:58.56,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In order to get rid of my image of being stuck up...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:58.56,0:08:59.76,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I did everything.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.69,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I always looked at the faces \Nof the people around me...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:02.69,0:09:04.54,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Always wary...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:05.57,0:09:06.67,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yet still...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:07.74,0:09:09.34,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why is everything about her?!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:49.36,0:09:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:51.03,0:09:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't worry. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:54.03,0:09:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Please head to the rehearsal.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:57.24,0:09:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:57.98,0:09:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:04.13,0:10:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's start the camera rehearsal, then!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's do a good job!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Here we go!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:09.42,0:10:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In five...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:10.38,0:10:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Four...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:11.26,0:10:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Three...
