Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:21.14,Myself TL (Episode 21),,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}Why... just why have I fallen in love with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:27.60,Myself TL (Episode 21),,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,1512)}Yet, still... I can't stop my tears from falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:46.75,Myself TL (Episode 21),,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}I lost way too much back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:51.13,Myself TL (Episode 21),,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}I couldn't sing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:55.59,Myself TL (Episode 21),,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}That place you had to leave for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:11:03.22,Myself TL (Episode 21),,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}It happened to be the place where I was
Dialogue: 2,0:10:54.09,0:10:57.59,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,430)}I wonder if they're talking about me.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.56,0:11:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Who was that?!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:05.85,0:11:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:06.43,0:11:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:07.86,0:11:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Cut the music!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:10.44,0:11:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How unbecoming...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:11.86,0:11:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Interrupting someone else's singing.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Komaki-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:17.45,0:11:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:18.93,0:11:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you are professional singers...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:20.95,0:11:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you should listen carefully and respectfully!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:24.36,0:11:25.70,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.29,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's just as you say, Komaki-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:28.01,0:11:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You too.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:29.41,0:11:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You were singing without any spirit.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:31.34,0:11:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:32.21,0:11:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where's that energy that you showed me?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And... you over there!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:39.26,0:11:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you have the time to sneak around behind someone's back...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:41.39,0:11:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...couldn't you at least learn how to put on a plausible act?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:43.86,0:11:45.24,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Madoka-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:45.77,0:11:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It looks like all you've been doing is spreading rumors...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't you have any real strength \Nto challenge her with?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:51.02,0:11:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If that's the case...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you've lost before you've even begun.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:54.53,0:11:55.92,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Madoka-san is... {\alpha&Hff&}spreading the rumors...? {alpha}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:55.92,0:11:57.13,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Madoka-san is... spreading the rumors...? {alpha}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:58.41,0:12:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}T-That's right!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:00.03,0:12:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We were just...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:00.99,0:12:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...taken in by what Madoka-san said.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:10.13,0:12:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I... may have done something unforgivable.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:14.34,0:12:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... I was jealous of {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:18.47,0:12:19.59,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Madoka-san is...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:19.59,0:12:21.05,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Jealous of me...?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:21.41,0:12:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But spreading rumors behind her back...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:24.43,0:12:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I had no intention of doing that.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:26.93,0:12:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just that...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:27.68,0:12:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...it seemed so nice to have someone you like...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:30.00,0:12:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I just wanted to have that too...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:31.52,0:12:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...just wanted to try liking somebody...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:34.53,0:12:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And just like that...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:36.03,0:12:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I would have never thought that it'd turn into such a huge rumor.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:41.28,0:12:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:42.61,0:12:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I didn't want it to be like this.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:45.12,0:12:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:48.21,0:12:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eichi-kun will surely find you.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:52.92,0:12:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:56.26,0:12:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Madoka might be a nicer girl than I thought... {she is, but that's later}
Dialogue: 2,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:00.55,0:13:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Because she couldn't say what she wanted to say.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I guess that works...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:05.01,0:13:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:06.34,0:13:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:09.31,0:13:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:12.44,0:13:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ow... ow... ow... {alpha is too distracting}
Dialogue: 2,0:13:13.43,0:13:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:14.60,0:13:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}T-That?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:15.63,0:13:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:16.19,0:13:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Did something happen?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:18.74,0:13:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What? What?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:21.32,0:13:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Who did such a horrible thing?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:25.08,0:13:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... hello?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is Ooshige.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:27.28,0:13:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is the stylist, Yasuno-chan, there?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:29.93,0:13:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:30.62,0:13:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's not?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:31.79,0:13:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do you know where she went?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:33.88,0:13:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:35.04,0:13:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's a huge problem with {\i1}Full Moon's{\i0}  costume!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... come on...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:40.04,0:13:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why is it that when something happens... I can't find anyone?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:43.67,0:13:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:51.69,0:13:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What was that?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:53.02,0:13:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Didn't she make it look like we were spreading the rumors?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:56.23,0:14:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Even though she was degrading {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}  herself...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:00.13,0:14:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's like she was just making up excuses.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:02.66,0:14:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Today's the first time I've truly understood just how scary show business can be.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:09.41,0:14:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just now...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What were they talking about?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:12.49,0:14:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Uh... that's...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's just as I thought.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:16.34,0:14:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:17.06,0:14:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What do you mean by that, Meroko?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:18.54,0:14:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Back there... Madoka's crying was just an act.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:21.84,0:14:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:22.55,0:14:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then... Madoka-san did this?!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:24.76,0:14:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Stop it.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:25.67,0:14:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We don't have any proof.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:27.47,0:14:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:28.83,0:14:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}After what we just overheard...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:30.55,0:14:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...what else am I supposed to think?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:32.96,0:14:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Saying that won't get us anywhere!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:35.92,0:14:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...we need to do something about this.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}T-That's right!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:40.23,0:14:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can't get a hold of Yasuno-chan!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:42.48,0:14:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:43.78,0:14:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Man, what am I supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:46.62,0:14:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's it!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:47.92,0:14:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:48.78,0:14:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This situation is a perfect chance for me to use my real power.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:52.16,0:14:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:52.53,0:14:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Real power?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:53.50,0:14:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's that?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:55.25,0:14:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:01.76,0:15:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mero Mero Change!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:08.39,0:15:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}T-This is a little...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:11.89,0:15:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}H-Huh... that's funny...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:14.39,0:15:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}One more try!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:19.85,0:15:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:20.94,0:15:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you just playing around?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:23.02,0:15:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We don't have much time...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:25.02,0:15:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}J-Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:31.83,0:15:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}H-Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:33.29,0:15:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:33.99,0:15:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(550,450)}{\an3}Ah... {ogles}
Dialogue: 2,0:15:34.25,0:15:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm begging you...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:35.59,0:15:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's only thirty minutes till she's up!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is strange...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:40.17,0:15:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}W-What's an idol's costume supposed to look like?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:43.09,0:15:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:43.75,0:15:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:44.17,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:45.67,0:15:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Some unknown person... \Nfor some unknown reason...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't understand why they would do this to my costume...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:49.64,0:15:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:50.47,0:15:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...despite the fact that someone did this...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:52.22,0:15:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I won't break down.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:07.03,0:16:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I said hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:08.70,0:16:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Have you lost it?!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Stop it! {\alpha&Hff&}Stop it! {alpha}
Dialogue: 2,0:16:13.35,0:16:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Stop it! Stop it! {alpha}
Dialogue: 2,0:16:14.33,0:16:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's wrong, Mitsuki?!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}At this very moment...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:22.41,0:16:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...she's probably freaking out about her costume.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's what you get...
