Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:32.93,Myself TL (Episode 21),,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}Why do I love you so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:38.76,Myself TL (Episode 21),,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}Your voice is calling out with such sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:45.19,Myself TL (Episode 21),,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}I never knew what was supporting me, back then, and even now
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:52.82,Myself TL (Episode 21),,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,840)}Until we became so far apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:06.46,Myself TL (Episode 21),,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}Why is it that I've fallen in love with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:16.55,Myself TL (Episode 21),,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,3500)}I can't find an answer easily...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:19.89,0:17:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Everyone...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:20.85,0:17:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}About what happened recently...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:21.97,0:17:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}By taking a vacation so suddenly...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I've caused many problems.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:25.36,0:17:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I... myself...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:29.39,0:17:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...will do my best from now on!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:31.56,0:17:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So... please treat me kindly!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:41.08,0:17:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That was good.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:42.58,0:17:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Though after seeing your last rehearsal...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:43.91,0:17:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I wasn't sure how things would turn out.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:46.09,0:17:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Keep up the good work!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:49.34,0:17:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:09.74,0:18:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Man...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:10.77,0:18:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I was surprised about the sudden costume change, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:13.61,0:18:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...it's good.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:14.82,0:18:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Your return to work was a big success, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:17.59,0:18:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:19.12,0:18:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well... it looks like some weird rumors were spreading, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:22.00,0:18:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:23.40,0:18:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It happens all the time in this business.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:25.62,0:18:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:28.09,0:18:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, then... let's keep it up!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:32.26,0:18:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Great job!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:35.22,0:18:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I never thought I'd see...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:36.18,0:18:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...your costume arranged like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:38.63,0:18:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Not in my wildest dreams.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:41.89,0:18:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The one who doesn't let a setback keep her down...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...is this little one here.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:45.72,0:18:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:46.77,0:18:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I had no idea what was going to happen today...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:49.10,0:18:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...but she toughed it out!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:51.40,0:18:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's for sure...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:52.90,0:18:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But you know...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:53.86,0:18:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...that Madoka...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:55.19,0:18:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I won't forgive her.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:56.70,0:18:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't say too much, Meroko.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:00.04,0:19:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I haven't heard much of the conversation, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:02.52,0:19:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...did something happen?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:03.74,0:19:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Someone tore her costume into shreds!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:07.04,0:19:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:07.66,0:19:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:08.79,0:19:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:09.88,0:19:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't worry about it, Wakaouji-sensei.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:12.41,0:19:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:14.00,0:19:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:16.17,0:19:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Something like this doesn't get me down at all!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:18.76,0:19:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}'kay?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:23.39,0:19:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki-chan... you really love to sing, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:25.97,0:19:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:27.10,0:19:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I understand.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:28.19,0:19:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I won't doubt you anymore.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:30.57,0:19:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wakaouji{\alpha&Hff&}-sensei... {alpha}
Dialogue: 2,0:19:31.96,0:19:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wakaouji-sensei... {alpha}
Dialogue: 2,0:19:35.32,0:19:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki-chan...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:36.36,0:19:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll find a way out of the surgery.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:39.53,0:19:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:40.53,0:19:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:42.41,0:19:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}However... don't push yourself too hard...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:44.79,0:19:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Coming back to work after so long...
