Dialogue: 2,0:19:49.86,0:19:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Really... don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:52.25,0:19:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:34.86,0:21:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh no! Oh no!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:36.23,0:21:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto, what should we do?!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:37.56,0:21:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you yelling about, Meroko?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:39.36,0:21:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Her first solo live concert has been scheduled, so...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:42.07,0:21:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...this isn't the time for that.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:43.24,0:21:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}As I was saying...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:44.53,0:21:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...there's a big problem with that live concert!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:46.99,0:21:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
