Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:59.09,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,100)}Why... just why have I fallen in love with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:05.55,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\be3\fad(200,200)}Yet, still... I can't stop my tears from falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:24.91,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(166,100)}I lost way too much back then
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:29.16,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,0)}I couldn't sing at all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:33.67,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,100)}That place you had to leave for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:41.26,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,0)}It happened to be the place where I was
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:47.64,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,100)}On that day I could see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:52.48,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,0)}The desolation lying in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:58.06,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,0)}I wonder if it's the same for both of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:05.49,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,0)}If you would just notice, I'm always by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:11.54,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(160,0)}Why do I love you so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:17.58,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(160,40)}Your voice is calling out with such sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:23.63,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(160,0)}I never knew what was supporting me, back then, and even now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:30.18,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,840)}Until we became so far apart...
